Q28. What is the output of the following code snippet?


	public class PrePostOperators {
	 
		 public static void main(String[ ] args) {
			 int x = 5;                                          // line 1
			 int y = ++x;                                        // line 2
			 int z = y++;                                        // line 3
			 
			 System.out.println("x=" + x + ", y=" + y + ", z=" + z); 
		 }
	}
	
